	Nag Champa soap can be used for a dull or oily complexion. It&nbsp;is said to have an&nbsp;anti-inflammatory, antiseptic, bactericidal and fungicidal action on the skin. It is cruelty free and it contains no animal fat, products or harsh chemicals. Its beautiful rich lather is a natural deodorant and wonderful skin softener which is also pH balanced and allergy tested. This is an original Nag Champa product from Satya Saibaba and is of super quality (beware of imitations). Nag Champa is a perfume originally manufactured in the Hindu and Buddhist monasteries of India and Nepal.</p>
